{"tid":202284,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"智慧牙其實係咪一定要\"mok\"?","createTime":"2017-04-15T11:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T21:16:52.000Z","uid":47864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bdbf34a94d6f205b7b1e79ac314354d9214adbad","tid":202284,"uid":47864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:30:40.000Z","msg":"牙咗我老母先。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實真係想問吓係咪要&quot;mok&quot;智慧牙？<br />\n我老豆老母話佢地都冇&quot;mok&quot;過，不過好快就爛晒。我聽講係因為唔覺有隻牙生咗出嚟，所以清理牙齒嘅時候會忽略咗隻智慧牙，長期以嚟就易蛀牙。<br />\n<br />\n之前一路想去&quot;mok&quot;都拖下拖下，拖咗成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢排3隻牙都生到出嚟，仲有一隻似係投緊胎過嚟團聚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問吓巴絲們係咪要&quot;mok&quot;?<br />\n有冇巴絲可以分享經歷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b811540c0716c755f8baa0ab605f58cf8f98dc72","tid":202284,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:38:15.000Z","msg":"其實佢生得正常 <br />\n冇打斜打橫生頂到其他牙 <br />\n唔剝都得<br />\n<br />\n點成日話有智慧牙就要剝<br />\n好多時係因為個口細唔夠裝 <br />\n當智慧牙生出嚟嗰陣<br />\n冇位出<br />\n就會頂住其他牙出<br />\n咁就唔剝唔得<br />\n<br />\n至於爛牙可能係因為太入 <br />\n擦得唔乾淨引起<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔想博<br />\n係佢開始出嗰陣<br />\n就去睇定牙醫<br />\n叫牙醫比專業意見你<br />\n<br />\n利申:剝咗3隻<br />\n老母係做牙醫助護"},{"pid":"42cc8cdd69dd740e1ca91c84b0391b3fb744ae89","tid":202284,"uid":72186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"剝完 過咗麻醉之後嗰種隱隱痛 好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbc5700bc83a37668ea2a576b4a22fe5988ee64","tid":202284,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:47:55.000Z","msg":"你去洗牙個陣 consult埋牙醫啦 佢答先最準確 每個人隻智慧齒生既情況都唔同"},{"pid":"76cfc3548b49ad8f3704d033cab10a889d6652e2","tid":202284,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:53:03.000Z","msg":"千五蚊一隻"},{"pid":"fd51339f31c5b67032b77dd38a8cd8ae8f78bb0d","tid":202284,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"大部份要剝係因為打橫生頂住左，難清理，易發炎<br />\n<br />\n利申：受害者"},{"pid":"f6f1ece19b4e2801f2a7f640e9c458b0ad2dac04","tid":202284,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:57:17.000Z","msg":"生左兩隻無剝<br />\n淨係生個時痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後無事了"},{"pid":"5ba2ad55700aba30452f9099dab08ec1084314aa","tid":202284,"uid":71378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:09:52.000Z","msg":"其實mok唔mok隻牙既重點係睇你有冇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">智慧</span></span>"},{"pid":"6df6718b1b7a3999eb9a239ad497b415b438a406","tid":202284,"uid":47864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T19:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千五蚊一隻</blockquote><br />\n就係窮所以拖吓拖吓就冇去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4隻mok晒要成6000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab56f752234e71235b85607d175e0983762a7b8","tid":202284,"uid":47864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T19:45:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢生得正常 <br />\n冇打斜打橫生頂到其他牙 <br />\n唔剝都得<br />\n<br />\n點成日話有智慧牙就要剝<br />\n好多時係因為個口細唔夠裝 <br />\n當智慧牙生出嚟嗰陣<br />\n冇位出<br />\n就會頂住其他牙出<br />\n咁就唔剝唔得<br />\n<br />\n至於爛牙可能係因為太入 <br />\n擦得唔乾淨引起<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔想博<br />\n係佢開始出嗰陣<br />\n就去睇定牙醫<br />\n叫牙醫比專業意見你<br />\n<br />\n利申:剝咗3隻<br />\n老母係做牙醫助護</blockquote><br />\n唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0105e17924ea54c747c4b986952ae6d9f463d73d","tid":202284,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci